模块 com.example.bubblebobble
程序包 com.ae2dms.model.scene

类 GameScene

java.lang.Object
com.ae2dms.model.scene.GameScene
public class GameScene extends Object
GameScene is an overall model(container for concrete model), its controller is GameSceneController, with GameScene.fxml as view. GameScene contains smaller model such as hero, enemy, fruit. it maintains a set of array of these smaller models, and when gameScene is initialized all these small models would be initialized.
